readmeContent.A_Star_Algorithm_Robotics_JAVA_C++:
# A* Algorithm for Robotics

This project implements the A* pathfinding algorithm for robotics applications in both Java and C++.

## Features

- Efficient pathfinding for robot navigation
- Obstacle avoidance
- Optimized for real-time applications
- Cross-platform implementation

## Technologies Used

- Java
- C++
- Robotics frameworks
